Changed behavior:
- MCP OAuth credentials now persist as the URL-bound flat record shape:
  { accessToken, refreshToken?, expiresAt, clientInfo, resource }.
- SDK OAuthTokens remain an in-memory boundary type only; McpOAuthProvider and
  McpRefreshManager translate to/from the persisted flat shape.
- Existing token-store guarantees are preserved: getAgentDir-derived path,
  mcp-auth/<sha256(serverUrl)>/tokens.json, directory 0700, file 0600,
  atomic tmp+rename writes, proper-lockfile read-modify-write locks, and
  index.json server-name -> hash mapping.

