Risks:
- The persisted shape intentionally no longer stores SDK token_type/scope/id_token.
  Provider.tokens reconstructs token_type="Bearer" for SDK callers. Current tests
  cover existing MCP OAuth fixture behavior and refresh races.
- clear() leaves an empty mcp-auth/index.json file when other server entries could
  exist; it removes the target server entry and credential dir, which is the
  server-specific trace required here.

